import React from 'react'
import { Nav } from 'react-bootstrap'
import { NavLink, Outlet } from 'react-router-dom'

export default function AdminHome() {
  return (
    <>
      <Nav variant="tabs" className="mb-4">
        <Nav.Item>
          <Nav.Link
            as={NavLink}
            to="/admin/medicos"
            className={({ isActive }) => isActive ? 'active' : ''}
          >
            Aprobar MÃ©dicos
          </Nav.Link>
        </Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Item>
          <Nav.Link
            as={NavLink}
            to="/admin/configurar"
            className={({ isActive }) => isActive ? 'active' : ''}
          >
            Configurar Roles
          </Nav.Link>
        </Nav.Item>
      </Nav>
      <Outlet />
    </>
  )
}
